"6 ounces thin-sliced apple wood- smoked or regular bacon (about 6 slices), cut into 3/4-inch pieces","2  onions (about 1 lb. total), peeled and chopped","3  cans (28 oz. each) Boston-style baked beans","1/2 cup catsup","2 tablespoons firmly packed brown sugar","1 tablespoon dry mustard"